{"tid":592224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[煙剷請入] 反對政府加煙草稅！","createTime":"2018-03-14T04:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T09:23:29.000Z","uid":145126,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"47211e29f05e77a8085e818c05874d3489d62eed","tid":592224,"uid":145126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"加煙稅即係逼人食<del>偲嫣</del>私煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該直接拉哂你班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n掟哂去咩喜靈洲小欖晨㬢島<br />\n同班癮君子、精神病人一齊鎖<br />\n逼你班仆街戒煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冚你家個富貴！<br />\n頭先喺德福想話放低幾両順便碌下連登<br />\n痾痾下就開始聞到煙味<br />\n個花灑又冇反應<br />\n個抽氣扇又唔知做乜尻唔抽走啲味<br />\n搞到我俾啲煙味攻到極想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔知係有人喺附近廁格食煙<br />\n定喺出面食然後啲煙抽入嚟啦<br />\n我淨係知你班仆街冚家產唔食煙<br />\n成個地球會清新咗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40dd63e4778b862ac736b938d3f46e3716488e70","tid":592224,"uid":173397,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:58:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77471ad15b5031726569dc8721bee3a61c1a2ef0","tid":592224,"uid":51076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T05:23:43.000Z","msg":"成撚日要吸二手煙真係好躁"},{"pid":"52ca3c015ef7ea2a3cdcf9800601b37d6e47f20e","tid":592224,"uid":145126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T09:22:10.000Z","msg":"火車頭固然罪該萬死！<br />\n但都唔可以放過其他煙剷<br />\n<br />\n每次聞到都好反胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99abf2f7aa474913278d1105f02418bf9a411788","tid":592224,"uid":145126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T09:23:29.000Z","msg":"都唔知啲人有乜好負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br 